{"build_type":"library","module_name":"enqueue-chunk-into-reclaim-ring","package_name":"enqueue-chunk-into-reclaim-ring","description":"Lock-free MPMC reclaim-ring enqueue (Vyukov + count give-back, no CAS). Gate on count BEFORE taking the enq position ticket (a position ticket cannot be given back): c=fetch_add(count,+1); if c>=capacity give the count back and return 0 (FULL -> caller keeps the chunk thread-local). Else take pos=fetch_add(enq,+1), wait the slot free (seq==pos), store the chunk ptr, publish seq=pos+1. Returns 1 enqueued / 0 full.","function_definitions":{"enqueue-chunk-into-reclaim-ring":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"ring_base","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"chunk","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"negone","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":-1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"cap","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4096},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"mask","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4095},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s24","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":24},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s16","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":16},{"instruction_type":"atomic_fetch_add","address":"ring_base","delta":"one","result_assignment_variable":"c","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":">=","lhs":{"value":"c"},"rhs":{"value":"cap"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"atomic_fetch_add","address":"ring_base","delta":"negone","result_assignment_variable":"_gb","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"enq_addr","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"+","target":"enq_addr","lhs":{"value":"ring_base"},"rhs":{"value":"s16"}},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"eight","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":8},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"+","target":"enq_addr","lhs":{"value":"ring_base"},"rhs":{"value":"eight"}},{"instruction_type":"atomic_fetch_add","address":"enq_addr","delta":"one","result_assignment_variable":"pos","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"slotidx","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"&","target":"slotidx","lhs":{"value":"pos"},"rhs":{"value":"mask"}},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"slotoff","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"*","target":"slotoff","lhs":{"value":"slotidx"},"rhs":{"value":"s16"}},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"slotbase","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"+","target":"slotbase","lhs":{"value":"ring_base"},"rhs":{"value":"s24"}},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"slot","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"+","target":"slot","lhs":{"value":"slotbase"},"rhs":{"value":"slotoff"}